Nora Lane https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nora_Lane 0 Nora Lane (September 12, 1905 – October 16, 1948) was an American film actress. She appeared in more than 80 films between 1927 and 1944. She shot herself dead one month after her husband died from a heart attack. Nora_Lane ( September_12_,_1905 – October_16_,_1948 ) was an_American_film_actress .
